
In /var/www/vhosts/harcuk.com/conf/vhost.conf:

<Directory /var/www/vhosts/harcuk.com/httpdocs>
php_flag register_globals on
</Directory>

and then I ran the following commands to incorporate the new changes:

[root@server2 ~]# /usr/local/psa/admin/sbin/websrvmng -av
[root@server2 ~]# service httpd reload
